compiling obfsproxy on Mac OS X 10.6
====================================

0) prelims

 a) autoconf 2.68

cd ~/src/autoconf-2.68
./configure --prefix=/usr && make
make check # takes a long, long time!
sudo make install 

 b) automake 1.11

cd ~/src/automake-1.11.1
./configure --prefix=/usr && make
sudo make install

1) obfsproxy

cd ~/src/DEFIANCE/code/obfsproxy
./autogen.sh
./configure
make


